think my plan worked. I self destructed and inceerated my base with megs 
inside. I think I did it! Ill have to wait to confirm it. Latley he seems to 
just keep comeing back like a masquito. Luckily my base held the only info on 
his spark signature ever so thankfullly no one can clone him again."
